data.description: Amazing level close in acreage property on private road in Brush Prairie! This home features 3 Bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Wood-burning fireplace with a brick mantel in the living room, perfect for cozying up during those cooler evenings. Soak up some sun in the generously-sized sunroom. Bright and airy with two sliding doors, it offers a seamless transition to the outdoors, making it a perfect spot for relaxation or entertaining. Whether you're preparing a feast or enjoying a quiet meal, this kitchen serves every purpose with New Built in double oven and lots of counter space. Functional mudroom equipped with a Washer & Dryer, Garage Access and adjacent 3/4 bath, it's designed to keep the outdoors out and your home clean. Master Suite features 3/4 Bath and Double Closets. Large Metal Outbuilding w/Power. Kid/Dog Friendly fencing around backyard & playhouse. Fresh produce is just a few steps away in the lovingly-tended vegetable and fruit garden, a treat for both novice and seasoned gardeners. The property comes equipped with secondary hookups, making it ideal for potential additional dwellings or utility needs. Well is 160' deep, also used for irrigation. Roof has 30 year transferable warranty! New gutters & downspouts. Refurbished well house. 1st Large Pasture on north side, 2nd Pasture on south side - both fenced & gated. The extensive acreage offers endless possibilities! Schedule your showing today! On border line of Battle Ground and Hockinson - possible exception for Hockinson schools! Buyer to do due diligence.
